project_path.GunfunnyToken: Experiments/contracts/GunFunny Smart Contract Audit Report - QuillAudits/GunfunnyToken

findings.title: No check or guard For renounceOwnership
findings.description: Contracts should have a double check for renounceOwnership function to prevent admin mistakenly calling the function and making the contract's admin address 0x000.

findings.title: Compiler Version/Flags Mismatch
findings.description: Contracts should be deployed using the same compiler version/flags with which they have been tested to prevent accidental deployment with older compiler versions that may contain unfixed bugs.
